snippet.title: 2021 Summer Academy Blooming Artist Concert #1
snippet.description:
Cheer on the students of ENCORE's 2021 Online Academy as they perform their solo repertoire!

Lucas Candelino - J.S. Bach (1685-1750): Violin Partita No. 3 in E major, I. Preludio.

Natalie Bryan - Edward Elgar (1857-1934): Concerto Op. 85, I. Adagio-Moderato. Alexis Zingale, piano.

Morgan Bennett - J. S. Bach: Violin Sonata No.2 in A minor, I. Grave, II. Fuga.

Erika Liu - Antonin Dvorak (1841-1904): Violin Concerto, I. Allegro ma non troppo. Chris Thompson, Piano.

Maya Irizarry Lambright - J. S. Bach: Violin Partita No. 2 in D minor, IV. Gigue.

Julian Casas - J.S. Bach: Cello Suite No. 3, I. Prelude.

Ciara McGuire - Eugéne Ysaÿe (1858-1931): Sonata No. 5 for Solo Violin, I. L'Aurore II. Danse Rustique.

Travon DeLeon - J.S. Bach: Violin Sonata No. 1 in G Minor, I. Adagio, II. Fugue.

Alex Fiszer - Luigi Boccherini (1743-1805): Concerto in Bb Major, I. Allegro moderato. Asela Zamorano, Piano.

Cassidy Walther - J.S. Bach: Cello Suite No. 3, IV. Sarabande.

Chanmin (Joel) Park - Gaspar Cassadó (1897-1966): Suite for Cello Solo, III. Intermezzo e danza finale.

Chanhee (Joy) Park - W.A. Mozart (1756-1791): VIolin Concerto in A Major, I. Allegro aperto. Sunny Suh, Piano.

Carlos Walker - J.S. Bach: Cello Suite No. 6, I. Prelude.

Kenny Fujii - Max Reger (1873-1916): Suite No. 1 in G minor for Solo Viola, I. Molto Sostenuto, II. Vivace, III. Andante sostenuto, IV. Molto vivace.
